<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Google Docs Comments</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }

        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .comment {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            padding: 15px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border-radius: 5px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .author {
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .timestamp {
            color: #777;
            font-size: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .content {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            text-overflow: ellipsis;
            display: -webkit-box;
            -webkit-line-clamp: 2;
            -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
        }

        .status {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #555;
        }

        .reply-comments {
            margin-top: 10px;
            padding-left: 20px;
            border-left: 2px solid #ccc;
        }

        .avatar {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin-right: 10px;
            background-color: #ccc;
            float: left;
        }

        .highlighted-content {
            border: 2px solid #ffcc00;
            padding: 5px;
            margin-top: 5px;
            overflow: hidden;
            text-overflow: ellipsis;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Google Docs Comments</h2>
        <div class="comment">
            <div class="avatar"></div>
            <div class="author">Ngo Tuan Anh</div>
            <div class="timestamp">17:43, 18 Mar (ICT)</div>
            <div class="content">
                @anhntgch220570@fpt.edu.vn testing function for assigning. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed vestibulum condimentum mi, nec consequat odio hendrerit eu.
            </div>
            <div class="highlighted-content">Highlighted content goes here. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.</div>
            <div class="reply-comments">
                <div class="comment">
                    <div class="avatar"></div>
                    <div class="author">John Doe</div>
                    <div class="timestamp">18:00, 18 Mar (ICT)</div>
                    <div class="content">Reply to the comment goes here</div>
                </div>
                <div class="comment">
                    <div class="avatar"></div>
                    <div class="author">Jane Smith</div>
                    <div class="timestamp">18:15, 18 Mar (ICT)</div>
                    <div class="content">Another reply to the comment goes here</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
